 was teaching in one of the synagogues on the Sabbath, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 4:31","book":"Luk","chapter":4,"verse":31,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 6:6","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 4:31","book":"Luk","chapter":4,"verse":31},{"label":"Lk 6:6","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Luk:13:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"a woman was there who had been disabled by a spirit "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit had a spirit of disability"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 8:17","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 4:33","book":"Luk","chapter":4,"verse":33,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 6:18","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 7:21","book":"Luk","chapter":7,"verse":21,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 8:2","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":2,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 8:29","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":29,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 9:39","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":39,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" for over eighteen years. She was bent over and could not straighten up at all. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or straighten up completely"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 8:17","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":17},{"label":"Lk 4:33","book":"Luk","chapter":4,"verse":33},{"label":"Lk 6:18","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":18},{"label":"Lk 7:21","book":"Luk","chapter":7,"verse":21},{"label":"Lk 8:2","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":2},{"label":"Lk 8:29","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":29},{"label":"Lk 9:39","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":39}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit had a spirit of disability"},{"marker":2,"text":"Or straighten up completely"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Luk:13:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When Jesus saw her, he called out to her, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Or he summoned her"},{"kind":"text","text":" “Woman, you are free of your disability.” "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Or he summoned her"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Luk:13:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then he laid his hands on her, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 19:15","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 5:23","book":"Mrk","chapter":5,"verse":23,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 6:2","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":2,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 6:5","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 8:23","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":23,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 4:40","book":"Luk","chapter":4,"verse":40,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" and instantly she was restored "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 15:16","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":16,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 12:12","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":12,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" and began to glorify God. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 11:4","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":4,"letter":"i"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 19:15","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":15},{"label":"Mk 5:23","book":"Mrk","chapter":5,"verse":23},{"label":"Mk 6:2","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":2},{"label":"Mk 6:5","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":5},{"label":"Mk 8:23","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":23},{"label":"Lk 4:40","book":"Luk","chapter":4,"verse":40},{"label":"Ac 15:16","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":16},{"label":"Heb 12:12","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":12},{"label":"Jn 11:4","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Luk:13:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But the leader of the synagogue, indignant "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 20:24","book":"Mat","chapter":20,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 21:15","book":"Mat","chapter":21,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 26:8","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 10:14","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 10:41","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":41,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 14:4","book":"Mrk","chapter":14,"verse":4,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" because Jesus had healed on the Sabbath, responded by telling the crowd, “There are six days when work should be done; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 20:9","book":"Exo","chapter":20,"verse":9,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 46:1","book":"Ezk","chapter":46,"verse":1,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" therefore come on those days and be healed and not on the Sabbath day.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 20:24","book":"Mat","chapter":20,"verse":24},{"label":"Mt 21:15","book":"Mat","chapter":21,"verse":15},{"label":"Mt 26:8","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":8},{"label":"Mk 10:14","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":14},{"label":"Mk 10:41","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":41},{"label":"Mk 14:4","book":"Mrk","chapter":14,"verse":4},{"label":"Ex 20:9","book":"Exo","chapter":20,"verse":9},{"label":"Ezk 46:1","book":"Ezk","chapter":46,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Luk:13:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But the Lord answered him and said, “Hypocrites!"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 6:42","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":42,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Doesn’t each one of you untie his ox"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 14:5","book":"Luk","chapter":14,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 14:19","book":"Luk","chapter":14,"verse":19,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 9:9","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" or donkey from the feeding trough"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 2:7","book":"Luk","